{
  "_comment": "Curriculum Schema v2 — Master Lesson Library model",
  "_architecture": [
    "1. lessons{} = global master library, keyed by stable lesson_id",
    "2. standard_course = 16 units, each with ordered lesson_id refs",
    "3. ap_course = 9 units (College Board), each with ordered lesson_id refs",
    "4. A lesson can appear in both a Standard unit AND an AP unit",
    "5. is_ap_only: true  → lesson is hidden in Standard view",
    "6. DB: lessons table stays as master; new unit_lessons junction table handles ordering per unit"
  ],

